description: I am a contractor for the Embassy-Air Wing. I work as a direct support Intelligence Analyst DYN. I provide route, venue threat and vulnerability assessments within the AOR. Also, I am responsible for briefing Officials on current enemy activity and events impacting or threatening Air operations. I evaluate counterterrorism threats, surface-air-fire events and threats, Indirect Fire threats and attacks, social structure, civilian demographics, paramilitary activity, religious sectarian affiliations, various local ethnicity, criminal and gang activity, and local media sentiment. Provided recommendations to exploit and or mitigate threats.
